  "detailed_description": "*** Dive in the beautiful and mysterious world with your Plasmorb! ***<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlasma orb is a marble-like game.<br />\r\nPlasmorb is a ball shaped creature that you are going to control<br />\r\nRoll your ball and go through different levels with mini-puzzles and narrow paths. And try not to break it and fall down!<br />\r\nYou will encounter many hindrances, mazes and mysterious constructions<br />\r\nAll the game levels look beautiful. You have to travel through an old forest, dangerous swamps and even explore the depths of underground!",
  "about_the_game": "*** Dive in the beautiful and mysterious world with your Plasmorb! ***<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlasma orb is a marble-like game.<br />\r\nPlasmorb is a ball shaped creature that you are going to control<br />\r\nRoll your ball and go through different levels with mini-puzzles and narrow paths. And try not to break it and fall down!<br />\r\nYou will encounter many hindrances, mazes and mysterious constructions<br />\r\nAll the game levels look beautiful. You have to travel through an old forest, dangerous swamps and even explore the depths of underground!",
